  "id": "M7N4aD7O",
  "slug": "timber-frames",
  "title": "Timber Frames",
  "description": "Build walls out of various timber frames and bring your medieval builds to the next level.",
  "body": "<p>A mod which adds various timber frame blocks and a tool to customize the shape of the frames using a connective texture system.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q8DrfTp.png\" alt=\"Banner\" width=\"772\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/70LnRIC.png\" alt=\"Timber frame house\" width=\"1024\" height=\"515\" /></p>\n<h1 align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fusion-connected-textures\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fusion</a> and <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/patchouli\" rel=\"nofollow\">Patchouli</a> are required for 1.20.1+ versions</strong></h1>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>(CTM is required for previous versions)</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SwQJ8q2.png\" alt=\"The broad knife and variants\" width=\"1125\" height=\"359\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wROwXNj.png\" alt=\"Wood types\" width=\"1374\" height=\"586\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YFmKXic.png\" alt=\"Variety of designs\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/XehqKbg.png\" alt=\"Tutorial (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kHeW76YEDlM\" height=\"469\" width=\"836\"></iframe></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uVtvgTs.png\" alt=\"The help menu\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1465\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/NEhSGvv.png\" alt=\"Crafting recipes (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/ZOhSYxl.png\" alt=\"The crafting recipes\" width=\"1024\" height=\"736\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/XTdgaJB.png\" alt=\"FAQ (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Issues &amp; Compatibility</strong></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Will there be a Fabric port?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">I hope so, it's high on the to-do list.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Are the 1.20.1+ versions compatible with previous versions worlds?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">No, Timber Frames for 1.20.1+ was re-written from the ground up to improve performance and maintenence.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What things have changed during the rewrite?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li>Various features have been changed and some have been (temporarily) removed to release as soon as possible, and we've shifted our connected textures handler from CTM over to Fusion.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li>This includes the removal of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>barn-related blocks, the isolation variant, natural generation of soul clay (now crafted from clay and soul sand), as well as change in recipe for the broad knife.</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li>Expect barn-related blocks to return eventually!</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Will this mod be available for version X?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jLQd2vq.png\" alt=\"idk\" width=\"310\" height=\"123\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Can I use Optifine?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li>Maybe, but I would advise against it. The recommended mods for performance/visuals are <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/embeddium\" rel=\"nofollow\">Embeddium</a> and <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/oculus\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oculus</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">If you have any bug reports, please leave them on our <a href=\"https://github.com/RasaNovum/Timber_Frames/issues\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Issue Tracker</a>.</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Features &amp; More</strong></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Are there any modded wood variants?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">No, but we're looking into using <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/every-compat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Every Compat</a> to allow for dynamic wood variant additions.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Are there any planned features?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">We're focusing on getting this version stable and releasing other mods, but we want to be able to expand the connection system and add new blocks in the future.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Can I use this in my modpack and/or server?</h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Yes, as long as it's downloaded from our official sources.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">What is Rasa Novum?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">We're a small group of mostly amateur developers making mods for our modpack and eventual server of the same name.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QSjVtfa.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"1200\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/V9V48Tt.png\" alt=\"Socials (title)\" width=\"1200\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.rasanovum.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dWKubWd.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/WGh4mq6W5U\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iGKNGA3.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/RasaNovum\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0gYQeJT.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rasa_Novum\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5h47qoo.png\" width=\"117\" height=\"96\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">If you're a fan of tightly designed mods like Timber Frames, try checking out our other mods for building and infrastructure like Ender Sender and Via Romana!</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Credits</strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Timber frame texture inspired by <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blockus\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blockus by Brandcraft</a>.</p>",
